flowchart LR

A[Document Input]
B[Chunking + Enhancement]
C[Embeddings + Storage]
D[Retrieval]
E[LLM Reasoning]
F[Response]

A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F

D --> G[Agentic Planner]
G --> E

E -->|Low Context| H[LLM Fallback]

